data.description: Welcome to your ideal family home, a beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom sanctuary in the heart of a family-friendly neighborhood, and just a stone's throw away from Whiteman Air Force Base. This property offers everything you've been looking for and more! The moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the open and airy design of this home. The living, dining, and kitchen areas flow seamlessly together, making it perfect for entertaining friends and family. With three bedrooms, there's plenty of space for a growing family. The spacious layout ensures that everyone in the family has their own private oasis to relax in. The master suite includes a beautifully updated bathroom, designed with modern touches and finishes. It's your personal retreat after a long day. No need to worry about parking or storage space. The attached two-car garage provides ample room for your vehicles and additional storage. Step outside to your spacious, fully-fenced backyard. This area is perfect for children to play, pets to roam freely, or for hosting summer barbecues with friends. Located in close proximity to Whiteman Air Force base, this home is perfect for military families or anyone who values convenience and easy access to work. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this house your home. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and experience the charm of this property for yourself!
